highlights.text: “It's the Most Wonderful Time of the Year” by Andy Williams is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 103 spots at #45.
J Balvin has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “RITMO (Bad Boys For Life)” is the highest at #10.
“Blinding Lights” by The Weeknd is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #7.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 152 weeks straight.
